content:
Add Flexibility to Data Cloud Filter and Join Nodes with All Map Fields

Filter and join nodes now support all Map Field data types in definitions that use the Data cloud runtime. This extended functionality brings the Data Cloud runtime in line with the CRMA runtime functionality in Data Processing Engine.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Data Processing Engine is enabled.
title: Enhancements in Salesforce Summer '24 Release
keywords: Data Cloud filter and join nodes
